com.mobius.vdrapi
Class ComparisonSpec

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.mobius.vdrapi.ComparisonSpec
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public final class ComparisonSpec
extends Object
implements Serializable

This class provides a list of available comparison values. It is distinct from SQLComparisonSpec, which should not be used unless specifically required by a particular class.

See Also:
